'''Ya̍p Â-Lòi''' ([[Yang-vun]]: Yap Ah Loy; [[fan-ti chung-vun]]: 葉亞來) hai [[Kat-lun-po]] yit ge fui-fau-kung-sin. Hi hai Chung-kok [[Kóng-tûng]] [[sén|saang]] Vai-chau Vai-yong ki Chhau-chhong chan ke [[Hak-kâ|Hak-ka-ngin]]. Yap Ah Loy lang-du Kat-lun-po chik du [[1880]] nin wan chang yi [[Yîn-koet|Yang-kok]] chik-man ching-fu wai chi.

